Python program to gather disseminated data from various resources (MyGene.info, NCBI Taxonomy, UniProt, etc...) and interact with Wikidata's API via PBB_Core.

MicrobeBotController.py
-controller for MicrobeBotModularPackage.py
USAGE: MicrobeBot_main.py <WD username> <WD password> <NCBI Taxonomy ID> <domain genes/proteins/encoder>

MicrobeBotDFunctions.py
-collection of Python functions for querying wikidata and creating reference objects for bot runs

MicrobeBotResources.py
-retrieves data for genes, proteins, and taxa from MyGene.info, Uniprot, and NCBI and returns a PANDAS dataframe

MicrobeBotGenes.py
-writes and edits microbial gene items in Wikidata

MicrobeBotProteins.py
-writes and edits microbial protein items in Wikidata